  "title": "Events Sales & Marketing Executive (Entry Level)",
  "description": "<p>We are looking for an ambitious <strong>Events Sales &amp; Marketing Executive (Entry Level)</strong> to help us increase our clients‘ Brand awareness and Customer base through the promotion of their products and services at our event sites in Singapore.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><strong>What You'll Do?</strong></p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>- Participate and ensure the successful execution of our events marketing campaigns</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>- Promote our products or services to existing and potential customers</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>- Work with the rest of the marketing team to develop promotion strategies and oversee their implementation</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><strong>Why Join Us?</strong></p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>- Fast tracked career progression/growth</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>- Uncapped income</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>- Traveling opportunities</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>- 1-on-1 coaching / mentorship</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><strong>Requirements</strong></p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>- Strong interpersonal and communications skills.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>- Sales, customer service or events marketing experience is a plus.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>- Strong organizational and project management skills.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>- Attention to detail and ability to multi-task.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>- Bachelor’s degree in Marketing, Business, or related field is a plus.</p>",
